    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>    Section of a configuration for grouping items.

    Constructor argument:
     - *doc* (*str*) --
       the name of this configuration section.

    A section can contain zero or more subsections and zero or more 
    configuration items.</verbatim> </para>    </detaileddescription>
